This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it focuses on text generation using variational autoencoders. Additionally, the paper also investigates multi-level structures to generate more informative latent codes and coherent long-term structures, which are relevant to the sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper may also be relevant to the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it discusses generating coherent long text, which is a task that can be applied to image captioning.
